congress dances is a 1932 german comedy film directed by erik charell and starring lilian harvey , conrad veidt and henri garat .   it was an english-language version of the german film der kongreß tanzt .   a separate french-language version le congrès s ' amuse was also made .   it is centered on the congress of vienna , where an austrian commoner is mistaken for the tsar of russia .   it was made at the babelsberg studio near berlin .   the film 's sets were designed by robert herlth and walter röhrig .